_refine.details                                  
;Molecular replacement search models were based on PDB entries 3ow8, 2hes, 3dm0 and modified using SCWRL and the FFAS03 server.
Programs Phaser and Molrep were used for molecular replacement.
Arp/warp was used for map imrpovement and automated model building.
Geometry restraints for the ligand were prepared with PRODRG based on GTG coordinates from PDB entry 3HXI.
Coot was used for interactive model building.
PHENIX.molprobity was used for geometry validation.
;
